{"tid":857029,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我計緊由零開始起一個香港出嚟要幾錢，有無巴打幫下手","createTime":"2018-10-11T01:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T14:03:48.000Z","uid":187905,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be15c1959b18987339563bf8e3c9676181044c12","tid":857029,"uid":187905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出於興趣，我想計下，由零開始起一個香港出嚟要幾錢<br />\n利申：我唔係咩學者，亦都唔係讀呢科，一定唔準確，但都想有個粗略估算，只可以做參考<br />\n<br />\n首先假設我地要搵一個地方起一個島<br />\n我參考左現代七大奇蹟Zuiderzee works<br />\n本身係一個防洪工程，因為個地區太低窪所以起左大提afsluitdijk 封住Zuiderzee , 抽晒入面d水，咁水位低左就多左個島, 人工島flevoland (970km sq) 仲差唔多成個香港加埋咁大(1104 km sq)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/fb/f6/8f/fbf68f8fad947e985f47d067427ad3ef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Ffb%2Ff6%2F8f%2Ffbf68f8fad947e985f47d067427ad3ef.png&h=71ccd68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南面綠色嘅就係flevoland<br />\n假設揾到一個咁嘅地方做一個差唔多嘅建設<br />\n<br />\n成本估算：<br />\nafsluitdijk <br />\n710m USD in 2004 = 948m USD in 2018<br />\n= 7.43b HKD <br />\n<br />\nDelta works<br />\n7b USD in 1997= 11b USD in 2018<br />\n= 86.2b HKD<br />\n<br />\n我就未揾到佢起個島出嚟要幾錢,定係已經包埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，可能我唔識荷蘭文揾唔到，或者有無其他例仔做合理估算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但淨係呢2樣已經 7.43 +86.2 = 93.63b 即係930億<br />\n<br />\n起完個島仲要起基建，當你淨係起最基本嘅<br />\n計起出嚟嘅成本，暫時唔計維持服務嘅成本住<br />\n暫時諗到有<br />\n水，污水：上面包埋水壩個d<br />\n煤<br />\n房屋<br />\n電<br />\n上網<br />\n交通：路，地鐵，公共交通工具？<br />\n<br />\n房屋<br />\n香港公屋平均355k 一個單位<br />\n我用355k 因為假設人工島大部份係平地，唔係插針式咁起，減少難度同成本<br />\n一個單位平均2.8個人住<br />\n一個人要用 355k/2.8 = 127k<br />\n假設700萬人有500萬人(大約70%)住公屋，其餘有錢人自己買(假設有地產商肯起樓)<br />\n127k * 5m = 635b 即係 6350億<br />\n<br />\n交易(道路)<br />\n香港有2101km 路<br />\n有145km係 高速公路<br />\n紐約2015<br />\n65k usd per mile = 318k hkd per km <br />\n318k * 2101 = 668m 即係6.68億<br />\n好似平左d，係咪用錯data<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好多未計，好多假設，覺得唔夠好可以提出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你想幫手計，d data 最好有汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nd sauce 我下面再放出嚟廢時咁長"},{"pid":"2702b902a23ac47cea26600ca62b296e178c4520","tid":857029,"uid":187905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T01:41:40.000Z","msg":"無人理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd46ce73f0314f817b5a9cef32c03850d1644f5","tid":857029,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T01:42:40.000Z","msg":"睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似好勁 總之唔使一百億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ef0174d65eb2ffd4c5652e031349e8abcd1842","tid":857029,"uid":187905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dd46ce73f0314f817b5a9cef32c03850d1644f5","tid":857029,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T01:42:40.000Z","msg":"睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似好勁 總之唔使一百億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"你係咪無睇清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"